         <p><a href="book-detail.shtml?bid=34">Squirm</a>, Carl Hiaasen's new book for young readers, was published Sept. 25.</p>
          <p>Carl delivers a wildly entertaining novel involving snakes, grizzlies, a missing dad, a menacing drone, and more!</p>

        <p> 
